      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Lemma isfullyfaithful_isfull_isfaithful_helper `{IsFull} `{IsFaithful}\n        (H' : forall x y (m : morphism set_cat x y),\n                IsEpimorphism m\n                -> IsMonomorphism m\n                -> IsIsomorphism m)\n  : IsFullyFaithful.",
